{"tid":1441061,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［方向］要令更多人支持我哋","createTime":"2019-08-10T14:46:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T15:02:38.000Z","uid":80592,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1741d770edeb1d71dd08b6ceba89c6ff8b2d15b1","tid":1441061,"uid":80592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T14:46:00.000Z","msg":"<pre><code data-type=\"\">雖然抗爭時間久了，但絕對不能忘記，\n我們一直以來的理念，一定要堅持下去。</code></pre><br />\n我之前都係一個CD-ROM 都無乜點發表過<br />\n今次第四次出post 如果有啲咩錯屌細力啲<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n做事手法好重要<br />\n對家文宣強咗 文宣要大大力做<br />\n要令更更更加多人加入我哋一方<br />\n記者會都係文宣嘅一種<br />\n對內：AirDrop同路人 行動 戰略 方向 文宣<br />\n對外：Facebook扮中立拉攏藍絲 放分化藍絲嘅文宣 WhatsApp forward都係重要嘅渠道<br />\n國際：機場派外文文宣 播英文片 最新派埋文宣USB<br />\n</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DrLgUUu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDrLgUUu.png&h=6550a2e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/28K11o3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F28K11o3.png&h=985d7652&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">冷靜思考 謀求對策</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">對準政權 勿生雜念</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求 缺一不可</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">光復香港 時代革命</span><br />\n</div></strong>"},{"pid":"19d3c827a2b774690d073c1efe27decba865a681","tid":1441061,"uid":80592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T14:47:39.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"309e3c67345e28d97ac626dd90b3d49ed36f3c22","tid":1441061,"uid":80592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T14:47:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.